snippet.title: SCP: Nemesi - Gameplay Highlights (Old Build)
snippet.description:
WISHLIST THE GAME NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2532230/SCP_Nemesi/

Publisher Build - Not final product, still under development 

SCP: Nemesi is an upcoming multiplayer survival horror set in the SCP Universe. Become a relentless SCP or take part in a team of 4 humans completing branching tasks in order to escape. The game takes place in different locations around the Earth and from different eras.
Official game site: https://scpnemesi.com/

00:00 SCP-173 
01:06 SCP-049 
02:34 SCP-106 
03:42 1v1 Gamemode
